'''Atrms n tafukt'''<ref>Amawal n tatrgit n Nijer</ref> nɣ '''Afsax n tafukt'''<ref>https://amawal.net/afsax</ref> nɣ '''Attwaɣ n tafukt'''<ref>http://www.amazic.cat/dictionary/eclipsi/ </ref> (s Tasrɣint : كسوف الشمس) iga yan wanaw n utrms azmz nna tlla [[Tafukt|tafukt]] d [[Ayyur|wayyur]] d [[Akal|wakal]] g yan umnid, ili wayyur ingr tafukt d wakal; mayad a ittadjan ayyur a iḥbs tifawt f wakal (ar gis ttilint tillas zund ukan iyyḍ).

[[File:Geometry of a Total Solar Eclipse.svg|thumb|Tawlaft ar gis ttbayan taɣarast n utrms n tafukt]]

Ur nzzḍaṛ ad niẓaṛ atrms n tafukt abla ig nlla g yan uḍɣaṛ iẓlin, acku atrms ar ittili ig tlla tafukt d wakal d wayyur g yan umnid, ɣikan ula afgan da isaqquln g tafukt, bac a iẓṛ atrms iqqand a ili g yan umnid d tafukt d wayyur. Ur ad saqquln kullu middn n umaḍal atrms, ar tsaqquln g kra n tmizar tiyyaḍ uhu.

